Package: DMRsegal
Type: Package
Title: Identify Differentially Methylated Regions from DMPs
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given   = "Vasileios",
           family  = "Lemonidis",
           role    = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email   = "vasileios.lemonidis@uantwerpen.be",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6446-3536")))
Author: Vasileios Lemonidis [aut, cre, cph]
Maintainer: Vasileios Lemonidis <vasileios.lemonidis@uantwerpen.be>
Description: DMRsegal implements a method for identifying Differentially 
    Methylated Regions (DMRs) from pre-computed Differentially Methylated 
    Positions (DMPs). The package uses a correlation-based approach to 
    expand regions around significant DMPs, considering both statistical 
    significance and biological relevance of methylation changes. It supports 
    both standard beta value files and tabix-indexed files for efficient 
    processing of large datasets.
